{"tid":37013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普惹惱中國，國民黨邱毅：都是蔡英文惹的禍","createTime":"2016-12-13T05:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T08:26:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6dcb5df4a4f234c57e5961da80fce66701b4fb","tid":37013,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1915651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1915651&d=GO2cYczxAjY3LJeNQy%2FbR2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=1bd3eac1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1915651&h=6cabc9c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1915651</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國民黨邱毅說川普要玩出火了，碰觸到中國的紅線，恐將闖出大禍。</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpSPkIA2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpSPkIA2.jpeg&h=ba6eb78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國民黨邱毅說川普拿「一中政策」當中美談判的籌碼，都是蔡英文那通電話惹的禍。</strong></span>（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpd2gfEq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpd2gfEq.jpg&h=d8a5b2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpU5rv9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpU5rv9W.jpg&h=a753dd80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統當選人川普（Donald Trump）11日表示，他完全了解「一中政策」，並且說：「我不知道為何我們必須被一中政策綁住」，此言一出引起各界關注，中國媒體還大力抨擊。前立委邱毅昨天在臉書上回應此議題表示，川普要玩出火了，以為中國是紙老虎，碰觸到中國的紅線，恐將闖出大禍。<br />\n<br />\n邱毅在臉書上表示，川普拿「一中政策」當中美談判的籌碼，將會惹怒中國，更危及中美關係及中國和台灣的關係。他批評川普在專業上無知、缺乏經驗，意識形態上偏激，對現實認識過時，因為勝利衝昏了腦袋，因此發生誤判，碰觸到中國最敏感的紅線，將闖出大禍。<br />\n<br />\n文章中還提到，總統蔡英文陶醉在那通電話的突破裡，但台海危機就已悄然逼近。因為台灣和中國兩軍實力懸殊，中共在很短的時間內就能夠拿下台灣。「蔡英文倚靠的美日根本發揮不了作用，當年俄羅斯與格魯吉亞的戰爭，就是很好的前車之鑒。」<br />\n<br />\n邱毅還提到，「蔡英文傳遞給川普團隊的信號，是台灣不承認九二共識、一個中國，大陸也沒能使台灣真正的地動山搖。」他還提到，川普誤判了形勢，竟異想天開地學蔡英文，想以「一個中國」和中國交換經貿利益，「所以歸根究底，還是蔡英文害慘了川普，都是那通電話惹的禍！」"},{"pid":"00433b82ce09b326d557b22d254245e138e5577e","tid":37013,"uid":5713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 又話台灣是中國一部分 打個電話都嬲嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7c289002f27474c332cea702c49bf93b5e9fda","tid":37013,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"會員侵入嚟講下"},{"pid":"ba64547eea9cae13382453df306c4b6baff15e44","tid":37013,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"應該即時將所有國民黨黨員送入監倉,全部當叛國賊處理"},{"pid":"ef4ecd85ed148a08e00edf80b97bcdd904e08248","tid":37013,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"Admin侵入一入黎"},{"pid":"9197b58d8f8c26b7c759abf6f2108587b26b7777","tid":37013,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"支那共匪B隊 -- 國民黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca27d179c6b2fd416afed7d015c29aa4b6316c2","tid":37013,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"美國佬講嘢又關蔡英文事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba9009da1a8232d05198b82d78ee31fcfb1ea0c","tid":37013,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"邱毅：<br />\n蔡英文不知道共產黨的底線，玩出火<br />\n<br />\n高登仔：邱毅你都戇鳩<br />\n<b