br />\n<br />\n但係台灣依家係中美角力 邊個贏邊個都未知</blockquote><br />\n原來過左火引狼入室咁大獲<br />\n咁仲講咩港獨，練咩體育救港，仲組熱血少年軍<br />\n軍隊WOR，軍隊唔打仗仲有咩做？<br />\n熱血仲唔摺左個熱血少年軍佢？<br />\n咁當初又講乜撚野左膠鳩做呀<br />\n我就係支持你熱普夠勇武，抗共最前線，我先投你黃洋達，twice呀！<br />\n<br />\n咁怕引狼入室就一於鳩做啦，繼續放三塊紕牌比人掉雞蛋啦啦！<br />\n<br />\n依家中共條底線係唔比講支那 HK is not china，我地就唔講。<br />\n第日佢底線係唔比講廣東話，我地又唔講？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a9553f485dece5f83e45b610b06a93b9c4d639","tid":37013,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邱毅：<br />\n蔡英文不知道共產黨的底線，玩出火<br />\n<br />\n高登仔：邱毅你都戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：<br />\n青年新政不知道共產黨的底線，玩出火<br />\n<br />\n高登仔：青年新政你都戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3m8g8i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3m8g8i.jpg&h=fa3a4c3f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢張圖我係佔領時期經常SEND比D 左膠朋友睇<br />\n當時我算係半隻熱狗，係我既大力軟性推銷下<br />\n佢地依家都接受左本土派，無一票投比保皇左膠，除左超區<br />\n但係估唔到今日睇返張圖竟然令我感到羞愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c53eb7a14f372b8ce86cd6674c80205851128d","tid":37013,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:11:49.000Z","msg":"錯啦國民黨<br />\n<br />\n明顯係蔣公剿賊不力嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced8b8b0f3f73badfd49ae4073a2540f28576bec","tid":37013,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"美國做野洗國民黨教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6d03efe9996277fa98abcae0c0a4d8334f2e43","tid":37013,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邱毅：<br />\n蔡英文不知道共產